snippet.title: Announcing Xbox Fitness
snippet.description: Work out smarter with famous trainers. Experience the world's best workouts with instant, personalized feedback, right in your home on Xbox Fitness. Train with Jillian Michaels, Tracy Anderson, P90X, Insanity and more. Optimize every workout with immediate feedback on your form, power and heart rate with the all new Kinect. Get unlimited access free with Xbox Live Gold for a limited time. Only on Xbox One.*
